name: Rosaria - LoRA
description:
LoRA trained from 50+ finely selected images on the internet. Best to use in combination with Anything V4.0.

Suggested LoRA weights: 0.5 ~ 0.9.

Suggested Img Size: 512x512/512x800/768x512

Tips:

Use in combination with control net plugin on in-game screenshots yield great results:

Initial draft may look underwhelming, please don't forget to use hires.fix to upscale your image (Denoising strength: 0.5 ~ 0.7)



(Minus the fingers :D)

Prompt words:

rosaria_\(genshin_impact\), bangs, crown, elbow_gloves, bare_shoulders, fishnet_legwear, cape, weapon,

Extra Fun Prompts:

Kimono, realistic, spear, weapon
